7 before the date of application of:
8 (A) a federal crime having a sentence of at least one (1) year;
9 (B) an Indiana Class A, Class B, or Class C felony (for a crime
10 committed before July 1, 2014) or a Level 1, Level 2, Level 3,
11 Level 4, or Level 5 felony (for a crime committed after June
12 30, 2014);
13 (C) a crime in a state other than Indiana having a penalty equal
14 to the penalty for an Indiana Class A, Class B, or Class C
15 felony (for a crime committed before July 1, 2014) or a Level
16 1, Level 2, Level 3, Level 4, or Level 5 felony (for a crime
17 committed after June 30, 2014);
18 (D) an Indiana Class D felony involving a controlled substance
19 under IC 35-48-4 (for a crime committed before July 1, 2014)
20 or a Level 6 felony involving a controlled substance under
21 IC 35-48-4 (for a crime committed after June 30, 2014); or
22 (E) a crime in a state other than Indiana similar to a Class D
23 felony involving a controlled substance under IC 35-48-4 (for
24 a crime committed before July 1, 2014) or a Level 6 felony
25 involving a controlled substance under IC 35-48-4 (for a crime
26 committed after June 30, 2014).
