SECTION 10. IC 7.1-7-1-2, AS AMENDED BY P.L.206-2017,
SECTION 3, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 2. The purpose of this article is to protect public
health and safety by:
(1) ensuring the safety and security of e-liquid manufactured for
sale in Indiana;
(2) ensuring that e-liquid manufactured or sold in Indiana
